          Hello! I am a passionate computing student dedicated to learning
          design and building immersive virtual worlds.
        </p>
        <img
          src="images/Brillantes.png"
          alt="Profile Picture"
          class="profile-pic"
        />
      </section>

      <section id="about" class="card about-card">
        <h3>About Me</h3>
        <p>
          <strong>Personal Information:</strong><br /><br />
          NAME: Brillantes, John David I. <br /><br />
          EMAIL: jhondavidbrillantes@gmail.com <br /><br />
          ADDRESS: St. Josep Village 3 Mamatid, Cabuyao, Laguna <br /><br />
          PHONE NUMBER: 09060969421 <br /><br />
          BIRTH DATE: July 29, 2007
        </p>
        <p>
          <strong>Education:</strong> <br /><br />
          Currently an IT student at the University of Cabuyao <br /><br />
